&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The BDM will manage opportunities through the sales lifecycle with guidance and support from the Head of Sales, working closely with delivery, and leadership teams to shape clear, client-focused propositions and ensure smooth handover&amp;nbsp;into&amp;nbsp;delivery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
